Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.64,0:00:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是原村啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年全國中學生大賽霸者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和  你的實力究竟如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我拭目以待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.48,0:00:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  小和
