Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她手上拿著的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:29.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}藤田職業選手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:32.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原村選手拿著的到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像是布玩偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:38.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}現在正進行檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學時沒見過她帶著這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.98,0:02:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:45.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只是個普通的布玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤田職業選手  為什麼是企鵝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹井久出的主意嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:03.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定是為了吸引眼球才那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼引人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:12.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好了  原村選手現在入席了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帶著那個打？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大受好評大受好評
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:20.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:23.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小和  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了受好評嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  這也是合宿時經過實驗所得的結論
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抱著艾托企鵝？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在家打線上麻將十分強勢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果抱著企鵝就能像在家裡一樣入睡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那打麻將時也抱著企鵝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會有在家裡打麻將時的水準
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有一半是為了製造話題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造話題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.17,0:03:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  和原本多次出現的低級失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在使用企鵝之後驟減
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子打線上麻將時最強
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網名小和和在線上麻將界被奉為傳說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說最強的原村和現在首次降臨在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家面前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}開始了  E桌副將戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:28.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}去年全國中學生大賽霸者  原村和的高中第一戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一巡就猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼可想的  打北風或九索就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局外人煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:49.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和和在打線上麻將時最先會稍微思考一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是思考不過也就4至5秒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但第二巡之後下手就不會猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手出牌時就考慮好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摸什麼牌打什麼牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算出所有組合類型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出快牌打亂我的步調嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點個役滿就有你好看的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.45,0:05:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我按平時步調打  剩下的交給大將就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張也不思考就出？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才打的六筒是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打一萬和牌的選擇更多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使考慮到四七筒剩下不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了容易和牌也該打一萬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  原村和一瞬間就決定留下一氣通貫的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您加點茶  透華大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤田職業選手  剛才打出六筒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每兩局獲得一次1000點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每三局獲得一次2000點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.33,0:06:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是持久戰你會選哪種呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2000點效率更高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和在一瞬間就判斷出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只考慮和牌率的人與連期望值都算進去的人相比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.97,0:06:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從結果來看差距是很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一般是不會去做一氣通貫的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從別家的棄牌判斷三萬還有剩餘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.77,0:06:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:35.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原村和率先立直了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本隊遙遙領先  還在這裡立直嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.71,0:06:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是選擇了比起防守拉大比分使全隊更為有利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說她不顧團體只為自我表現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事與願違啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.69,0:06:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在第八巡打掉一萬就一發自摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小咲  要吃墨西哥餅嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:58.76,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第一局  流局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:01.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有聽牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有聽牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和也不過如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  她沒特別引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但剛才的打法和判斷速度簡直就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上遇到的小和和一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和中學時代的牌譜中就隱約能看出一點影子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但從她現在的打牌風格能清楚的看出…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小和和的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  逆轉的好牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大三元！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.29,0:07:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斷幺寶牌1
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2900點加上一本場3200點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一個非門清的斷幺竟把我的大三元給白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那噁心的企鵝是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下帶寶牌三筒的兩坎不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場內已經三張二筒了你們看不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.31,0:08:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三色三同順寶牌2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12000點加上二本場12600點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:56.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}千曲東  12000點的點炮代價太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千曲東完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是原村和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但原村登場以前分差不就已經很大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽你這麼一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道清澄很強？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.99,0:09:22.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然她就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人1300點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.85,0:09:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和連莊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局勢或許要一邊倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在其它三所學校為了做大牌而束手束腳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也跟不上和的速度了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每人3000點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.71,0:10:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小和和！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}副將戰  結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:53.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}清澄高中副將原村和  以壓倒性的速度獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:57.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄突破第一輪已經是板上釘釘的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤田職業選手  看了原村和的比賽您有何感想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:12.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我大吃一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟原來的她完全不在一個檔次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那契機會是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.27,0:11:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企鵝…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.37,0:11:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出大事了！出大事了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透華
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原…原村和  果然是小和和！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在說這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和中學時代的牌譜簡直判若兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:54.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的原村和打牌99%是小和和的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不能壓倒性獲勝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.98,0:12:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你可真有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  原村和是副將所以會跟透華碰面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰才是真正的偶像  來一分高下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也得清澄能撐到決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣  衣還沒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你看了那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村和？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是原村…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村之後出場的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大將？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  第五個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙超厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會工夫就把東福寺打成負分結束了比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.23,0:12:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的第五個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是第五個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:52.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:01.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（午休  女子團體賽第二輪14：00開始）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  慶祝清澄高中麻將部突破第一輪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時向著第二輪勝利這一目標  乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.15,0:13:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.85,0:13:25.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（墨西哥餅裡真暖和）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過小咲真是嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把東福寺打成負分結束比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那個是…你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原村同學還有之前的各位已經把分數降到很低了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東福寺在大將戰開始時還剩46800點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說今天和不認識的人打牌很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:13:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想…還想和強者比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜進入第二輪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤田職業選手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那不是解說的藤田靖子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤田職業選手去搭話的是清澄高中！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:19.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬排飯小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天要打敗你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解說的名人跑到這裡來偷懶不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:29.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對那邊兩位有點興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位與之前簡直判若兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這十天時間裡到底施了什麼魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為某人的手下敗將才最有效吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.56,0:14:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但即使接下來贏了下午的第二輪進入決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得遭遇龍門渕和風越
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:14:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍門渕的天江強得一塌糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風越今年也是最強陣容
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.54,0:15:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為不會像初戰那麼順利了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有那麼棘手嗎  這兩所學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:19.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第二輪馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:23.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}各校的先鋒請到指定位置集合
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那麼出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女孩…或許能脫胎換骨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是作為大將就很遺憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使能進入決賽  對手可是天江衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許在那一局就會被毀得體無完膚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:15:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空蕩蕩的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午誰都不會來看我們的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.14,0:16:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕大部分人都去看從第二戰開始登場的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩所種子學校  龍門渕和風越的比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位  都準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備受矚目啊  大受矚目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…為什麼讓我來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話是不想叫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替衣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說衣沒來的話你就是大將
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣真是個讓人操心的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5台鬧鐘全滅了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少感覺上要跟衣相近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  小步是登記過替補的  應該沒有大問題才對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你這身打扮是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從宅邸直接趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:09.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  我是透華大人的女僕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透華的專屬可是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真要出場了  就穿我的衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:30.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大小姐  不…透華學姐的衣服給我穿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說透華的專屬女僕是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.23,0:17:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  代替衣大人還是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:40.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第二輪  A桌  先鋒請準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步  安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有換衣服的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天龍門渕出場的…只要我一個人就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}開場前倒數10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:18:00.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}9  8  7  6  5
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:04.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}4  3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二輪  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  部長也真會使喚人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這個時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是風越  那麼多觀眾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不打麻將了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:29.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}勝負已定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:32.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}第二戰H桌  結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}風越女子壓倒性的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:39.32,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那支傳統強隊風越回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕鬆取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風越好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就戰勝了上屆第三的城山商業
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅如磐石鐵板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年龍門渕也危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.58,0:18:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次或許是歷代最強的五人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著說  接著說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天也要像今天這樣加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風越嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…她可真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（風越女子高等學校休息室）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼鬆懈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:16.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的比賽算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為作為隊長的你那麼磨磨蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下邊的人才會那麼打牌的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才打七筒是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為對手太弱就沾沾自喜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種沒出息的打法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為在全國大賽上能管用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年你也是這麼搞砸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經忘了當初點炮一個倍滿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我們優良傳統上抹黑這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的失誤是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怪就怪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田在校內排名第二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:20:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與畢業學姐的練習賽裡獲勝率達到了31%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰選手還包括久保教練您在內
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.19,0:20:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮到分差剛才的打法我認為是最合理的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且去年龍門渕的天江衣有魔鬼附身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是我也可能給她點炮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:25.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她這一年應該都在自責
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為她感到驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等回去要好好開會反省啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.69,0:20:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘三所學校是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘三所學校定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  定下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A區獲勝的是龍門渕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.08,0:21:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…先鋒戰就將蓧之井西打成負分取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先鋒井上純在南場坐莊時一口氣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下進入決賽的還有鶴賀學園和清澄高中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.53,0:21:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩所似乎都是首次打入決賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍門渕獲勝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍門渕輸了的話  就不能直接向她們復仇了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.85,0:21:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要讓教練  龍門渕  比賽對手和觀眾們都見識一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…這所風越女子才是最強的
